    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>then add<strong> </strong>your<strong> fish sauce</strong> – this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p>",
